🕸‍ *Sniper*:  
  
▪️ Sniper has a gun and some bullets(With respect to number of the players) to kill mafias.  
  
▪ if the sniper shots a non mafia player, the sniper will be killed.  
  
▪️ Sniper cannot kill the godfather.  
  
▪️ if the sniper shots a mafia and doctor does not save that mafia, the mafia will be killed.  
   
▪️ if you shot a mafia and the doctor save that mafia, the mafia will stay in the game.  